BFN 

  [Text] Alija Izetbegovic, president of the state 
presidency, accompanied by Army General Rasim Delic, chief of 
general staff of the Army of the Republic of Bosnia-Herzegovina, 
and Minister for Internal Affairs Bakir Alispahic, is visiting 
Herzegovina. On his way to Mostar, Izetbegovic on 27 June 
visited several military bases of the 4th Corps. Commanders of 
this formation of the Bosnia-Herzegovina Army briefed 
Izetbegovic on the military and security situation and the 
results achieved in the implementation of the Washington 
agreement. At the recruitment center of the 4th Corps of the 
Bosnia-Herzegovina Army, Izetbegovic addressed the first 
generation of Herzegovina recruits. 

